Image Generation Prompt:
"A modern, minimalist logo for a high-end designer clothing brand, designed in a clean vector style suitable for fashion branding. The logo features an abstract, geometric monogram-style mark combining sharp angular lines with one fluid curved element, symbolizing sophistication and creativity. Color palette: a rich emerald green paired with a bold mustard-yellow accent, used in a balanced 70/30 ratio to keep the design elegant rather than loud. The mark should feel premium, timeless, and scalable — working equally well as a small tag on clothing and as a large storefront sign. Typography (if included) should be a modern sans-serif or thin-weight custom lettering, uppercase, with generous letter spacing for a luxury feel. The overall composition should be symmetrical or have refined balance, set on a clean white or transparent background, with no gradients, no photorealistic elements, no clutter — flat design, high contrast, negative space used intentionally. Style reference: contemporary fashion-house branding (avant-garde, boutique, editorial) — original and distinct, not resembling any existing brand logos. Deliver as a clean, isolated vector-style icon suitable for embroidery, print, and digital use."

A few things worth deciding before generating:

Do you want a wordmark (brand name in stylized text), a symbol/icon only, or a combination mark (icon + text)?
Any specific brand name or initials you'd like reflected in the design?

Let me know and I can tighten the prompt further, or I can render a first visual draft of this logo directly if you'd like to see options.

