Website Generation Prompt:
"Design a modern, elegant e-commerce website for a fashion brand that creates contemporary, designer, and customised clothing for all age groups. The site should feel premium yet approachable — blending boutique sophistication with everyday usability.
Structure & Pages:

Homepage with a hero banner showcasing seasonal/featured collections, a brief brand story section, and category highlights (Men, Women, Kids, Customised)
Inventory/Shop page with filterable product listings (by category, age group, size, color, price) and a clean grid layout with hover-preview effects
Individual product pages showing multiple images, size/color selection, price, availability, and an 'Add to Cart' / 'Buy Now' flow
A dedicated 'Customisation' page where users can request tailored/made-to-order clothing, including a simple form or step-by-step configurator (fabric, fit, measurements, style preferences)
A 'Consultation' feature allowing customers to book a styling/design consultation — via a calendar-based scheduling widget or a request form connecting them with a stylist
Cart and secure checkout flow supporting standard sale/purchase transactions
About, Contact, and Customer Support pages
User account area for order history, saved items, and consultation bookings

Design Style:

Subtle, muted color palette (soft neutrals like sand, ivory, sage, or muted taupe — avoid loud or saturated colors) with one understated accent tone for CTAs
Clean modern typography — a refined serif for headings paired with a minimal sans-serif for body text
Generous white space, high-quality product photography as the visual focus, minimal decorative clutter
Smooth micro-interactions (hover effects, subtle transitions, fade-ins) to keep the experience interactive without feeling busy

Technical Requirements:

Fully responsive design that adapts seamlessly across mobile, tablet, laptop, and desktop screens (mobile-first approach)
Intuitive, accessible navigation with a simple menu structure, clear breadcrumbs, and prominent search bar
Optimized for performance and scalability to handle high concurrent user traffic (efficient image loading, caching, lazy-loading for product grids, CDN-ready architecture)
Secure checkout and payment integration, with clear trust signals (SSL, payment icons, return policy visibility)
Original design system — do not replicate the layout, visual identity, or component styling of any existing fashion e-commerce website; the design should feel distinct and true to this brand's own identity.

Overall tone: understated luxury, effortless usability, and a shopping experience that feels personal — especially given the customisation and consultation offerings."

